snippet.title: Blood Omen: Legacy of Kain: Trailer
snippet.description:
Sporting one of the greatest story lines in video game history, The Legacy of Kain series has confused thousands of fans and tortured players for decades. Awesomeness ensues.

This series will not go live for a while, but the production is nearly complete, so it is definitely going to happen. I am just waiting for my MLG schedule to clear up a bit.
